START FIELD UNIT

Initialize ESP32
Initialize BME280
Initialize Rain Sensor
Initialize ESP32-CAM
Initialize LoRa
Initialize LED
Initialize Siren

LOOP FOREVER

    Read Temperature
    Read Humidity
    Read Pressure
    Read Rain Sensor

    Package Data:
    {
        Temperature,
        Humidity,
        Pressure,
        RainStatus
    }

    Send Data via LoRa

    IF RainStatus == TRUE THEN
        Turn ON LED
        Turn ON Siren
    ELSE
        LED OFF
        Siren OFF
    END IF

    Wait 30 seconds

END LOOP
